THE GAME
--------

  'Flog' is a Workbench game, it is based on the solitaire game
'Golf'. The game shows 7 columns of 5 cards. A card (the 'next'
card), facing up is shown at the bottom of the game window. At the
left of that card is a pack of the remaining cards and that pack
is face down.

  The goal of the game is to empty all 7 columns of cards by
clicking on cards that can follow or precede by one unit the card
at the bottom of the window. For example, if the card is a 5 of
Hearts, the choosen card should be a 4 or a 6, the colour or type
of figure has no importance. In this game a King can follow an Ace
or vice versa.

  Have fun!

